The paper discusses a research framework for mining scientific publications using Apache Hadoop, which involves classification, categorization, and citation matching of scientific publications. This suggests that the paper could belong to several sub-categories related to information retrieval (cs.IR), data mining (cs.DL), databases (cs.DB), machine learning (cs.LG), and natural language processing (cs.CL).
